# Emitted proof obligations are run-outputs of
#   python -m mycelium_experiments.vsa_bounds --proof --emit-obligations
# They are regenerated per sweep (and are empty unless the sweep has in-regime
# points), so they are NOT committed. The committed scaffold is README.md +
# cabal + src/ (the LH skeleton) + lean/ (the Lean 4 skeleton).
# To keep a representative populated obligation from a real GPU run, add it
# explicitly with `git add -f`.
*-multihop-*.smt2
*-multihop-*.hs
*-multihop-*.lean
*PROOF-SUMMARY.md
# Lean 4 build outputs (lake build artifacts)
lean/.lake/
lean/lake-manifest.json
